===============
Modules 016
===============
Modules are constants

module Transportation
  def going_forward
    puts "going forward"
  end
end

either include modules or extend modules

include - methods become instance methods
extend - methods become class methods
---------------------------------------
Example:
class Car
  include Transportation
end
  c = car.new
  c.going_forward
--------------------------
class car
  extend Transportation
end
  Car.going_forward
----------------------------------------


